Chesapeake Bay Mind & Body Smart Diffuser allows you to create your own wellness environment using WiFi, ultrasonic technology, lighting and mist. Now, Chesapeake Bay works with Amazon Alexa, providing the convenience of voice control to turn your Smart Diffuser on and off, change light color, and more!

After connecting Alexa to your Chesapeake Bay products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Chesapeake Bay" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Chesapeake Bay account in our "Chesapeake Bay" app;
(3). You need to have some Chesapeake Bay devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Chesapeake Bay app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Chesapeake Bay" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Chesapeake Bay" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Chesapeake Bay", and you'll be navigated to Chesapeake Bay login page;
(9). Input your Chesapeake Bay account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

Now enjoy the convenience of smart home fragrancing with Alexa voice commands such as:
“Alexa, turn on Smart Diffuser” 
“Alexa, turn off Smart Diffuser”

To learn more about Chesapeake Bay Smart Diffuser, visit yankeecandle.com/chesapeakebaycandle
